title: Natura Sound Therapy 3.0+key_crack
description:
Natura Sound Therapy v3 | 49.8 Mb 


Natura Sound Therapy software is the ideal tool to improve your quality of life. You can quickly achieve states of relaxation or concentration with Natura. Featuring 34 nature and music sounds and many special visuals, Natura can help you concentrate for work or study, unwind and relax, or even fall asleep more quickly. Natura gives you instant access to customized mood enhancement with unique presets of sounds, colors, and visuals.

? Version 3 features: 24 new sounds added, relaxation module added, Full featured brainwave synchronizer added, 38 factory presets added brainwave visual added, 12 video visuals added, color picker added, new background images added, visual and audio plug-in capability added, and timer with chime or alarm added.
